    <p>
        The Globalstar network has the worst coverage of the three (<a href="http://findmespot.com/coverage">see coverage map here</a>).
        Like Iridium, it is privately owned, but does not have good coverage of the poles, parts of sub-Saharan africa, and other regions.
        Why consider it?  It's worth a look if you know you are only traveling in areas with service and are looking for a cheaper option.
    </p>
